00:19:30.701 --> 00:19:32.270
Jantungmu akan meledak.

00:19:33.004 --> 00:19:34.171
TIDAK.

00:19:34.505 --> 00:19:37.174
Itu karena Anda menekan terlalu keras.

00:19:37.174 --> 00:19:38.509
Tenang saja.

00:19:39.644 --> 00:19:40.478
Oke.

00:19:41.946 --> 00:19:43.581
Sekali lagi.

00:19:44.215 --> 00:19:45.850
Menghirup.

00:19:46.684 --> 00:19:47.585
Menghembuskan.

00:19:48.119 --> 00:19:49.320
Detak jantung Anda...

00:19:52.256 --> 00:19:55.660
(Ruang Ganti Wanita)

00:19:57.728 --> 00:19:59.196
Aku gila.

00:19:59.196 --> 00:20:01.198
Aku benar-benar gila.

00:20:02.333 --> 00:20:03.301
Brengsek.

00:20:03.768 --> 00:20:06.270
Mengapa jantungku
berdebar kencang di sana?

00:20:13.544 --> 00:20:15.846
Jadi seorang teman mabuk naik taksi pulang,

00:20:15.846 --> 00:20:17.148
dan ketika aku bertanya, "Kamu mau pergi ke mana?"

00:20:17.148 --> 00:20:18.449
- "Aku pulang," katanya.
- Aku mengerti.

00:20:18.449 --> 00:20:20.518
"Tapi kami minum di rumahmu."

00:20:23.054 --> 00:20:24.622
- Itu lucu sekali.
- Jadi...

00:20:24.622 --> 00:20:26.557
Dokter Byeon, Anda sangat lucu.

00:20:26.857 --> 00:20:29.594
Apakah saya cemburu sekarang?

